The Dispatch Registrar has received an open commission from the Covenant Council for an expedition-grade survey of the Void Citadel. The structure's interior is poorly documented in current reference archives, and any expedition planning into the Citadel requires complete navigation data before crews can be committed. Chart every accessible section and return with a full navigation record.
Your Void Citadel survey has been filed with the Covenant Council's expedition archive. The navigation record is now the primary reference for any commission work tied to the Citadel, and the Dispatch Registrar has marked the commission fulfilled in the Covenant's open contract ledger.

